All Implemented Interfaces:
CreatesMustCallForElementSupplier, org.checkerframework.javacutil.AnnotationProvider
public class MustCallAnnotatedTypeFactory extends org.checkerframework.common.basetype.BaseAnnotatedTypeFactory implements CreatesMustCallForElementSupplier
The annotated type factory for the Must Call Checker. Primarily responsible for the subtyping rules between @MustCall annotations.

    • withoutClose

      public AnnotationMirror withoutClose(@Nullable AnnotationMirror anno)
      Returns a @MustCall annotation that is like the input, but it does not have "close". Returns the argument annotation mirror (not a new one) if the argument doesn't have "close" as one of its elements.

      If the argument is null, returns bottom.

      Parameters:
      anno - a MustCall annotation
      Returns:
      a MustCall annotation that does not have "close" as one of its values, but is otherwise identical to anno

      public org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFStore getStoreForBlock(boolean afterFirstStore, org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.block.Block first, org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.block.Block succ)
      Fetches the store from the results of dataflow for first. If afterFirstStore is true, then the store after first is returned; if afterFirstStore is false, the store before succ is returned.
      Parameters:

      Returns:
      the appropriate CFStore, populated with MustCall annotations, from the results of running dataflow
